## Step 5 — Create All the Files

Now create each file manually in the right folder. Here's exactly where each file goes:
```
backend/
├── server.js                          ← create this
├── .env                               ← already done
├── package.json                       ← already done
├── config/
│   └── supabaseClient.js              ← create this
├── middleware/
│   └── authMiddleware.js              ← create this
├── controllers/
│   ├── authController.js              ← create this
│   ├── studentController.js           ← create this
│   ├── scholarshipController.js       ← create this
│   └── applicationController.js      ← create this
└── routes/
    ├── authRoutes.js                  ← create this
    ├── studentRoutes.js               ← create this
    ├── scholarshipRoutes.js           ← create this
    └── applicationRoutes.js           ← create this